data.description: Incredible historic farm home situated on 36.52 acres. Formerly the Keller Tree Farm, this immaculate token of history boasts peaceful living and beautiful scenery. Enjoy the sights and sounds of several streams running through the property. The home has been meticulously maintained and includes two bedrooms with two full bathrooms. Also included are three sheds and a large garage barn.
